lead_paragraph: England have retained Semesa Rokoduguni and Marland Yarde in a 25-man squad as they prepare for Saturday's final test of the autumn series against Australia at Twickenham.

headline.print_headline: England's Rokoduguni, Yarde Retained for Australia Clash
